Vedanta’s Konkola Unit Installs Generators in Zambia Amid Power Shortages

-- B y   A n t h o n y   M u k w i t a
-- 
2011-06-15T08:41:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-15/vedanta-s-konkola-unit-installs-generators-in-zambia-amid-power-shortages.html
Vedanta Resources Plc (VED) ’s Konkola
Copper Mines unit in Zambia has installed three diesel
generators with a capacity of 24 megawatts at its Konkola Deep
Mining Project to provide emergency power back-up.  Konkola commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
